Team GB supporters in the UK, with daily coverage to run all the way through to the closing ceremony on Sunday, August 11.\", \"from\": 331, \"to\": 532, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 410, \"end\": 417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9993960004528266, \"rank\": 0.00043008063582539966, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 436, \"end\": 438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999680822975915, \"rank\": 2.0766178304932126e-05, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the action\", \"from\": 347, \"to\": 357}, {\"ngram\": \"air\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 390}, {\"ngram\": \"television\", \"from\": 395, \"to\": 405}, {\"ngram\": \"daily coverage\", \"from\": 445, \"to\": 459}, {\"ngram\": \"the closing ceremony\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 510}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 520}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 528}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And unlike in Tokyo three years ago, or Rio in 2016, the time difference will stand at just one hour - meaning those keen to follow will not have to stay up through the night or set any alarm clocks in order to watch the drama live.Express Sportgives you the lowdown on how you can follow the Games in France\\u2026.\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 844, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 548, \"end\": 553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999996261027432, \"rank\": 2.096934712362774e-06, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 836, \"end\": 842, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9872646030124614, \"rank\": 0.005319098532220927, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time difference\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 606}, {\"ngram\": \"just one hour\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 634}, {\"ngram\": \"the night\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 708}, {\"ngram\": \"any alarm clocks\", \"from\": 716, \"to\": 732}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 741}, {\"ngram\": \"the drama\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 760}, {\"ngram\": \"Express Sportgives\", \"from\": 766, \"to\": 784}, {\"ngram\": \"the lowdown\", \"from\": 789, \"to\": 800}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 832}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pick up your ultimate guide to the Olympics!\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 890, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your ultimate guide\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 873}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 889}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Going for Gold provides the day-by-day rundown of what's on and when.\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 960, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gold\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 905}, {\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 929}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Clickhereto buy.\", \"from\": 961, \"to\": 977, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Clickhereto buy\", \"from\": 961, \"to\": 976}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Once again in the UK, theBBCis the official Olympic television broadcaster, but like with Tokyo 2020 it will not be a case of both Beeb channels showing live action at the same time.\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 1161, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 997, \"end\": 999, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999680822975915, \"rank\": 2.0766178304932126e-05, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"db