/resource/Television_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1368, \"end\": 1372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Two\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"BBC2\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Two\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Two\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The sports\", \"from\": 1257, \"to\": 1267}, {\"ngram\": \"viewers\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1335}, {\"ngram\": \"the news\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1386}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For those who arrive home late having been unable to watch during the day can catch the nightly highlights show at 10.40pm.\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1517, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1467}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Beeb will also provide coverage online and via the radio.\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1580, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Beeb\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1527}, {\"ngram\": \"coverage\", \"from\": 1546, \"to\": 1554}, {\"ngram\": \"the radio\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1579}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The BBC iPlayer Olympics Extra will stream events running from 8am until approximately 11pm at night, and there will be an Olympics Extra channel available on BBC iPlayer, Red Button and online.\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1585, \"end\": 1588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.6130215564097977, \"rank\": 0.6312612342734399, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}, {\"begin\": 1589, \"end\": 1596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_iPlayer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"iPlayer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_iPlayer\", \"